          "type": "IMG"
        },
        {
          "id": "aba4c52f6728_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "3ff1",
          "text": "Daniel is currently working on a long- term project to turn the island of Majorca into a prototype for the bioregional transition towards diverse regenerative cultures, adapted to the biocultural uniqueness of place.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "aba4c52f6728_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "164e",
          "text": "Daniel’s book ‘Designing Regenerative Cultures’ explores ways in which we can\nreframe the current crises and re-design the human impact on Earth from being degenerative and exploitative to being regenerative and healing.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
